RITUALE json_expect_obj(Json j) REDDE SPECULUM NIHIL
  QUANDO j
    CASO JsonObj(h):
      REDDE OBSECRO json_handle_ptr(h)
    CASO JsonNull:
      IACE "json: expected object"
    CASO JsonBool(v):
      IACE "json: expected object"
    CASO JsonNum(v):
